<head>MORALITY</head>
    <list type="translations">
        <item xml:lang="zh">倫理道德</item>
    </list>
<div type="definition">
<p>VIRTUE of REFLECTING SYSTEMATICALLY on WHAT IS GOOD ACT:act AND a GOOD LIFE.</p>
    </div>
<div type="notes">
<div type="old-chinese-criteria">
<p>衷 could perhaps just as well be classed under EARNEST. The notions of morality and earnestness are closely related. This needs further study.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
